"      Guilleminault C, Shergill RP. Sleep-disordered Breathing in Neuromuscular Disease. Curr Treat Options Neurol 2002; 4:107.",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li>",
"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"UTD.htm?1/22/1382/abstract/5\">",
"      Krachman SL, Criner GJ. Sleep and long-term ventilation. Respir Care Clin N Am 2002; 8:611.",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
